---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import benPortrait from '../assets/images/ben-portrait.jpg';
import benCasual from '../assets/images/ben-casual.jpg';
import benHeadshot from '../assets/images/ben-headshot.jpg';
import benStanding from '../assets/images/ben-standing.jpg';
---
<Layout
  title="About Benjamin"
  description="Meet Benjamin, founder of Jonroc. 15 years of real business operations, from running 35+ employees in an event rental company to building AI automation for growing businesses."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 pt-32 pb-20 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
      <!-- Radial glow -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 30%, rgba(201,168,76,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-16">

          <!-- Photo -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="relative">
              <!-- Gold glow -->
              <div
                class="absolute -inset-3 rounded-3xl opacity-25 blur-2xl pointer-events-none"
                style="background: #C9A84C;"
                aria-hidden="true"
              ></div>
              <Image
                src={benPortrait}
                alt="Benjamin Johnstone, founder of Jonroc"
                width={300}
                height={400}
                format="webp"
                quality={85}
                class="relative w-[240px] h-[320px] md:w-[300px] md:h-[400px] rounded-2xl border-2 border-[#C9A84C]/40 shadow-2xl shadow-black/60 object-cover"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Headline copy -->
          <div class="text-center md:text-left">
            <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-5 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
              Founder &amp; Operator
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#F0F0F0] leading-tight mb-5">
              Meet <span class="text-[#C9A84C] gold-text">Benjamin</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#9CA3AF] max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
              15 years of hands-on business operations, from managing 35 employees in the field to installing AI agents that handle the work teams shouldn't be doing manually.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Story -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
      <!-- Section divider -->
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/20 to-transparent mb-20" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          The Story
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-12 leading-tight">
          From Sweeping Floors to<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          <span class="text-[#C9A84C] gold-text">Running the Operation</span>
        </h2>

        <!-- Story block 1 -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase">The Beginning</h3>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed text-lg mb-4">
            Benjamin started his professional career on the ground floor of his family's event rental business. Literally, he started by sweeping warehouse floors, then moved up to dishwashing, and progressed through every position in the company until he arrived at General Manager.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed text-lg">
            For four years as General Manager, he ran daily operations for a company with over 35 employees and staff. He learned every part of the business: scheduling crews, managing inventory, handling customers, keeping the books straight, and dealing with the thousand small fires that come with running a service business.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="w-16 h-px bg-[#C9A84C]/30 mb-12" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <!-- Story block 2 -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase">A Problem Worth Solving</h3>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed text-lg mb-4">
            During that time, Benjamin discovered that a local web design company was overcharging his family's business for website work and online marketing. Young and stubborn enough to do something about it, he taught himself web development and took over the company's digital presence. That side project became a passion.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Two years later, with his family's blessing, Benjamin stepped away from the rental business to launch Jonroc full-time. Since 2011, Jonroc has served clients across the country, building websites and running marketing campaigns for businesses in construction, events, professional services, and more.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="w-16 h-px bg-[#C9A84C]/30 mb-12" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <!-- Story block 3 -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase">Seeing the Pattern</h3>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed text-lg mb-4">
            But the industry changed. Every business now runs on a stack of software tools that were supposed to make things easier, but mostly just added more screens to check. Benjamin saw the same pattern over and over: companies paying for a dozen subscriptions, teams copy-pasting data between platforms, and owners still doing manual work that should have been automated years ago.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed text-lg mb-4">
            And then there was the marketing problem. Every company Benjamin worked with had the same story. Online marketing ideas would come up in meeting after meeting. Everyone agreed they were important. A new social media strategy, a better website, an ad campaign that could bring in real leads. But nothing ever got done. And when something finally did get launched, nobody could tell you whether it actually worked. The return on investment was always a mystery. Thousands of dollars spent, and the best anyone could say was "we think it's helping."
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed text-lg">
            The 15 years Benjamin spent in both the rental industry and digital services gave him something most AI consultants don't have: a deep understanding of how real businesses actually operate, from the warehouse floor to the back office. He's not selling technology for technology's sake. He's solving the same problems he used to deal with himself, just with better tools. And that includes the marketing side. Because a business that runs great operations but can't measure its own marketing is still leaving money on the table.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="w-16 h-px bg-[#C9A84C]/30 mb-12" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <!-- Story block 4 -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase">Where Jonroc Is Today</h3>
          <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Today, Jonroc works primarily with construction companies and event businesses, two industries where complex logistics and high-volume operations make AI automation especially impactful. Benjamin's approach is straightforward: show up, understand the operation, install what works, and stay around to make sure it keeps working.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative max-w-md w-full">
            <!-- Gold glow behind image -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%); filter: blur(12px); transform: scale(1.05);" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <!-- Gold border wrapper -->
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl p-[2px]" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.7) 0%, rgba(201,168,76,0.15) 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.6) 100%);">
              <img
                src="/images/ben-graffiti.jpg"
                alt="Benjamin Johnstone, founder of Jonroc"
                class="rounded-2xl w-full object-cover shadow-2xl block"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why AI Agents -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#111111] relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Background glow -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      ></div>
      <!-- Top border accent -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/60 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          The Pivot
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-6 leading-tight">
          Why <span class="text-[#C9A84C] gold-text">AI Agents?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Benjamin didn't pivot to AI because it was trendy. He pivoted because he kept seeing the same exhaustion in every business he worked with, capable teams buried in repetitive, low-value work that no software subscription was actually fixing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Jonroc still builds websites and runs online marketing campaigns. That hasn't changed. What has changed is how. Now, every website we build and every marketing campaign we run is powered by AI agents underneath. The agents handle the repetitive work: document processing, customer communication, quote generation, reporting, campaign monitoring. They do it automatically, around the clock, and better than a human doing it manually ever could. We install the agents first. Then we build and manage your digital presence on top of that foundation. You get the full package, operations and marketing, both running on AI.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-14">
          It's not technology for technology's sake. It's the same problem Benjamin's been solving since he was a 20-something running a rental crew, just with tools that didn't exist back then.
        </p>

        <!-- Three pillars -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold mb-2">Real Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-sm leading-relaxed">15+ years operating and managing real businesses, not just consulting from the sideline.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17 17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0 0 21 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 1 1-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 0 1-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-6.336 4.486c.091 1.076-.071 2.264-.904 2.95l-.102.085m-1.745 1.437L5.909 7.5H4.5L2.25 3.75l1.5-1.5L7.5 4.5v1.409l4.26 4.26m-1.745 1.437 1.745-1.437m6.615 8.206L15.75 15.75M4.867 19.125h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold mb-2">Purpose-Built</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-sm leading-relaxed">No off-the-shelf chatbots. Every agent is built and configured around your specific operation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.59 14.37a6 6 0 0 1-5.84 7.38v-4.8m5.84-2.58a14.98 14.98 0 0 0 6.16-12.12A14.98 14.98 0 0 0 9.631 8.41m5.96 5.96a14.926 14.926 0 0 1-5.841 2.58m-.119-8.54a6 6 0 0 0-7.381 5.84h4.8m2.581-5.84a14.927 14.927 0 0 0-2.58 5.84m2.699 2.7c-.103.021-.207.041-.311.06a15.09 15.09 0 0 1-2.448-2.448 14.9 14.9 0 0 1 .06-.312m-2.24 2.39a4.493 4.493 0 0 0-1.757 4.306 4.493 4.493 0 0 0 4.306-1.758M16.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold mb-2">We Stay Around</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-sm leading-relaxed">Installation isn't the end. Benjamin stays engaged to make sure the agents keep working as your business grows.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- CTA -->
    <CTASection
      heading="Ready to"
      headingHighlight="Talk?"
      subtext="One conversation. No pitch deck. Just an honest look at your operation and where automation actually makes sense."
      buttonText="Book a Discovery Call"
      footnote="No commitment. No pressure."
    />

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
